        <text><![CDATA[ASSET DETAIL WORKSHEET]]></text>
      </element>
      <element kind="staticText" x="160" y="160" width="80" height="20">
        <text><![CDATA[Undeposited funds are cash or checks not yet deposited into an account, and the amount of any temporary cash funds that may exist.]]></text>
      </element>
      <element kind="staticText" x="160" y="180" width="80" height="20">
        <text><![CDATA[Enter the total amount below with the reason it is not in a bank.]]></text>
      </element>
      <element kind="staticText" x="160" y="200" width="80" height="20">
        <text><![CDATA[4th quarter only: Also enter any undeposited transfer checks written in prior year.]]></text>
      </element>
      <element kind="staticText" x="160" y="220" width="80" height="20">
        <text><![CDATA[UNDEPOSITED FUNDS AND LATE-ARRIVING TRANSFER CHECKS]]></text>
